             sworn. I am a journeyman baker, I live with 
               <persName id="t18061029-38-person401">
                  Thomas 
                  Cox
               <interp inst="t18061029-38-person401" type="surname" value="Cox"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18061029-38-person401" type="given" value="Thomas"></interp>
